    "body" : "<p>Have you seen this Coding Horror blog entry?</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.codinghorror.com/blog/archives/001218.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">The Sad Tragedy of Micro-Optimization Theater</a></p>\n\n<p>I am not shure whether or not it is \"neater\", but from a performance-standpoint it probably won't matter much.</p>\n"
