    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Your approach is dependent on Java's ArrayList#toString() implementation.</p>\n\n<p>While the implementation is documented in the Java API and very unlikely to change, there's a chance it could. It's far more reliable to implement this yourself (loops, StringBuilders, recursion whatever you like better).</p>\n\n<p>Sure this approach may seem \"neater\" or more \"too sweet\" or \"money\" but it is, in my opinion, a worse approach.</p>\n"
  }, {
