    "body" : "<p>A variation on codefin's answer</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static String concatStringsWSep(Iterable&lt;String&gt; strings, String separator) {\n    StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();\n    String sep = \"\";\n    for(String s: strings) {\n        sb.append(sep).append(s);\n        sep = separator;\n    }\n    return sb.toString();                           \n}\n</code></pre>\n"
