      "body" : "Yup, every time: Bloch, &quot;Effective Java&quot;, Item 47: &quot;Know and use the libraries&quot;.  The Apache Commons libraries should be the first thing to put in your build file (hopefully Gradle).  As Item 47 concludes: &quot;To summarize, don&#39;t reinvent the wheel&quot;."
