    "body" : "<p>Using Java 8+</p>\n<pre><code>String str = list.stream().collect(Collectors.joining())\n</code></pre>\n<p>or even</p>\n<pre><code>String str = String.join(&quot;&quot;, list);  // Substitute &quot;&quot; with your desired separator.\n</code></pre>\n"
