    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are developing for Android, there is <a href=\"http://developer.android.com/reference/android/text/TextUtils.html#join(java.lang.CharSequence,%20java.lang.Iterable)\"><code>TextUtils.join</code></a> provided by the SDK.</p>\n"
