    "creation_date" : 1452093371,
    "answer_id" : 34636530,
    "question_id" : 523871,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In java 8 you can also use a reducer, something like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static String join(List&lt;String&gt; strings, String joinStr) {\n    return strings.stream().reduce(\"\", (prev, cur) -&gt; prev += (cur + joinStr));\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
